1.5
log
@Change lsearch()'s "base" argument to require a non-const pointer to
align with POSIX and other systems.

Pointed out by Elliott Hughes on tech
ok deraadt
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: lsearch.c,v 1.4 2009/10/27 23:59:59 deraadt Exp $	*/

/*
